U.S. Sassuolo Calcio|Sassuolo]]\n|{{flagicon|Italy}}\n|align=left|29 January 2014\n|align=left|3 March 2014\n| 6 || 0 || 1 || 5 || {{#expr: 0/6 * 100 round 2}} ||3||9||\u22126\n|-\n! colspan=4 style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"|Total\n! 614 !! 232 !! 192 !! 190 !! {{#expr: 232/614 * 100 round 2}} !!801!!711!!+90\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Managerial===\n;Chievo (1993\u20131997)\n*[[Lega Pro Prima Divisione|Serie C1]] (1): [[1993\u201394 Serie C1|1993\u201394]]\n\n;Parma (1998\u20132001)<ref name=auction/>\n*[[Coppa Italia]] (1): [[1998\u201399 Coppa Italia|1998\u201399]]\n*[[UEFA Europa League|UEFA Cup]] (1): [[1998\u201399 UEFA Cup|1998\u201399]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]] (1): [[1999 Supercoppa Italiana|1999]]\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of UEFA Cup winning managers]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.hellastory.net/pages/scheda.cfm?id=7D590D79-4854-12EA-BD663F99594DEB70 Profile of Alberto Malesani on Hellastory.net]\n\n{{UEFA Cup / Europa League winning managers}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Alberto Malesani managerial positions\n|list1=\n{{A.C. ChievoVerona managers}}\n{{ACF Fiorentina managers}}\n{{Parma F.C. managers}}\n{{Hellas Verona F.C. managers}}\n{{Panathinaikos FC managers}}\n{{Udinese Calcio managers}}\n{{A.C. Siena managers}}\n{{Bologna F.C. 1909 managers}}\n{{Genoa C.F.C. managers}}\n{{U.S. Citt\u00e0 di Palermo managers}}\n{{U.S. Sassuolo Calcio managers}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Malesani, Alberto}}\n[[Category:1954 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Verona]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:UEFA Cup winning managers]]\n[[Category:Udinese Calcio managers]]\n[[Category:Parma Calcio 1913 managers]]\n[[Category:ACF Fiorentina managers]]\n[[Category:Modena F.C. managers]]\n[[Category:Panathinaikos F.C. managers]]\n[[Category:A.C. ChievoVerona managers]]\n[[Category:Empoli F.C. managers]]\n[[Category:Robur Siena managers]]\n[[Category:Bologna F.C. 1909 managers]