e-welle-launches-global-news-channel Deutsche Welle launches global news channel - Broadband TV News], 22 June 2015</ref> The 24-hour service aims to establish a German counterpart to international news channels from other countries like [[BBC World News]] or [[France 24]]. The service is transmitted worldwide via [[satellite]].\n\n== Availability ==\n\nIn America, DW News can be received via cable and satellite TV broadcast. A 30-minute program similar to the ''[[Journal (Deutsche Welle)|Journal]]'' is available on many stations that are [[PBS]] members. The 30-minute program is also available nationwide on [[Link TV]].<ref>[http://www.dw.com/en/usa/a-19479685 Service reception in the USA], 17 August 2016</ref> Also, it is available on [[YouTube]] as DW English.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.guynews.tk |title= How to do }} Wednesday, 28 August 2019 </ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[DW-TV]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}UUUU\n\n[[Category:24-hour television news channels in Germany]]\n[[Category:German television news programs]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n", "text_old": "{{for|the American-based Chinese language news outlet|Duowei News}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name            = DW News\n| image                = DW_News_titlecard.jpg\n| caption              = title card\n| show_name_2          =\n| genre                = [[News program]]me\n| creator              =\n| writer               =\n| director             =\n| creative_director    =\n| developer            =\n| presenter            = Various\n| starring             =\n| voices               =\n| narrated             =\n| country              = [[Germany]]\n| language             = [[German language|German]]<br />[[English language|English]]<br />[[Spanish language|Spanish]]<br />[[Arabic language|Arabic]]\n| num_seasons          =\n| num_episodes         =\n| list_episodes        =\n| executive_producer   =\n| co_exec              =\n| producer             = [[Deutsche Welle|DW]]\n| supervising_producer =\n| asst_producer        =\n| co-producer          =\n| editor               =\n| story_editor         =\n| location             = [[Berlin]]\n| cinematography       =\n| camera               =\n| runtime              = 3, 15, 30, or 60 minutes\n| network              = [[Deutsche Welle|DW]]\n| picture_format       =\n| audio_format         =\n| first_run            =\n| first_aired          = 22 June 2015\n| last_aired           = present\n| preceded_by          =Journal News<br>Journal Nachrichten<br>Journal Noticias<br>\n| followed_by          = \n| related              = \n| website              = http://www.dw.com/en/tv/dw-news/s-3232\n| production_website   =\n}}\n\n'''DW News''' is a global English-language news and information channel from [[Germany|German]] international broadcaster [[Deutsche Welle]] (DW).\n\n== History ==\nDW News was launched on 22 June 2015 and superseded other international DW programs like the ''[[Journal (Deutsche Welle)|Journal]]''.<ref>[http://www.broadbandtvnews.com/2015/06/22/deutsche-welle-launches-global-news-channel Deutsche Welle launches global news channel - Broadband TV News], 22 June 2015</ref> The 24-hour service aims to establish a German counterpart to international news channels from other countries like [[BBC World News]] or [[France 24]]. The service is transmitted worldwide via [[satellite]].\n\n== Availability ==\n\nIn America, DW News can be received via cable and satellite TV broadcast. A 30-minute program similar to the ''[[Journal (Deutsche Welle)|Journal]]'' is available on many stations that are [[PBS]] members. The 30-minute program is also available nationwide on [[Link TV]].<ref>[http://www.dw.com/en/usa/a-19479685 Service reception in the USA], 17 August 2016</ref> Also, it is available on [[YouTube]] as DW English.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.guynews.tk |title= How to do }} Wednesday, 28 August 2019 </ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[DW-TV]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:24-hour television news channels in Germany]]\n[[Category:German television news programs]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n", "name_user": "223.196.169.218", "label": "vandal", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DW_News"}
